column5: Conveniently located 1 bedroom 1 bath option with easy access to major highways such as 380, Dallas North Tollway, 121/Sam Rayburn Tollway, 75 & I-35.  Apt has patio with quaint courtyard view, community gym accessible 24/7 and an outdoor pool. Pet-friendly with pet stations outside for potty breaks. Best available Thursdays and 1st/3rd/5th Fridays-Sundays.
column8: Quaint with quick access to local hotspots!
